rewarded_spend.rewarded_spend_information_message_intro: The Reward Road is a monthly reward program where every month, Trainers can earn Reward Points with eligible purchases on the Pokmon GO Web Store or in-game shop* Earn a certain amount of Reward Points to increase the Reward Road level and unlock rewards!
rewarded_spend.rewarded_spend_information_message_bulle: Make a purchase on the Pokmon GO Web Store or in-game shop to earn Reward Points*
Earn enough Reward Points and Trainers can unlock rewards
Visit the Pokmon GO Web Store to claim unlocked rewards**
rewarded_spend.rewarded_spend_information_message_aster: *Please note that purchases must be made with real money. Purchases made using PokCoins will not grant Reward Points.
**Rewards can be claimed on the Pokmon GO Web Store when a Trainer is logged into their Pokmon GO account. An account must be in good standing to claim Rewards.
rewarded_spend.rewarded_spend_information_message_body1: Each Reward Road lasts for one calendar month. Reward Points and Reward Road levels will reset on the last day of the month at 11:59 PM UTC so be sure to claim your rewards before the end of the month!***
rewarded_spend.rewarded_spend_information_message_body2: While Trainers can earn Reward Points in the Pokmon GO app, Trainers receive additional points for purchases within the Pokmon GO Web Store.
rewarded_spend.rewarded_spend_information_message_aster: ***Please note, Reward Points expire at the end of the calendar month. Even if a Trainer claims every reward, Reward Points will not carry over between months. Trainers using child accounts are not eligible to participate in the Rewards Road program. Reward Points are not cash or any other currency, and are non-transferable between accounts. Reward Road program availability and terms are subject to change.

rewarded_spend.rewarded_spend_information_message_body1: Each Reward Road lasts for one calendar month. Reward Points and Reward Road levels will reset on the last day of the month at 11:59 PM UTC so be sure to claim your rewards before the end of the month!***
rewarded_spend.rewarded_spend_information_message_body2: While Trainers can earn Reward Points in the Pokmon GO app, Trainers receive additional points for purchases within the Pokmon GO Web Store.
rewarded_spend.rewarded_spend_information_message_aster: ***Please note, Reward Points expire at the end of the calendar month. Even if a Trainer claims every reward, Reward Points will not carry over between months. Trainers using child accounts are not eligible to participate in the Rewards Road program. Reward Points are not cash or any other currency, and are non-transferable between accounts. Reward Road program availability and terms are subject to change.
